    0
  ],
  "variable_placeholders": "Single shallow Victorian brass pressure gauge authored facing south (+Z). Case depth follows Create's boiler gauge proportion at approximately 3 units for a 14-unit face. All textures and UVs use one pixel per model unit. steam_pressure_gauge.png contains the brass front bezel at x=0..15 and plain finished rear casing at x=16..31. steam_pressure_gauge_dial.png is the separate inset dial plate. steam_pressure_gauge_needle.png is dedicated to the animated needle, counterweight, and fixed hub. Rotate the needle group around local Z at [8,9,9.03], from -135 degrees at zero pressure to +135 degrees at burst pressure. The included animation is preview-only. No frequency controls are designed into this art source.",
  "resolution": {
    "width": 16,
    "height": 16
  },
